    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... it feels like I've lost all my agency. i'm just a passenger in a body that's failing me, waiting for something to happen to me. i hate just sitting here waiting for the inevitable. i wish i could just be the one to decide when the time is right, instead of just waiting for things to get worse.",
